OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,FThe Netherlands captain Virgil Van
OL,7,FDijk has criticised FIFA's new
OL,8,Fmandatory cooling breaks in the 2026
OL,9,FWorld Cup.
OL,11,FSpeaking after his team's 2-2 draw
OL,12,Fagainst Japan on Sunday, the defender
OL,13,Fsaid that the three-minute breaks
OL,14,Fimplemented into each half of every
OL,15,FWorld Cup game should not be
OL,16,Fmandatory, but should be considered on
OL,17,Fa game-by-game basis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,F"Hydration breaks are a bit
OL,7,Finteresting, because I was obviously
OL,8,Fwatching almost all the games up until
OL,9,Ftoday, and every time going to
OL,10,Fcommercial is a bit ... Not really
OL,11,Fthat I like it," he said.
OL,13,F"I think for the neutral watchers on
OL,14,FTV it's also not great. If it's really
OL,15,Fhot, obviously, it would be good to
OL,16,Fput them in. But I think you have to
OL,17,Flook at it in every game, separately,
OL,18,Fin my opinion."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
