FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,FFIFA has maintained that the hydration
OL,7,Fbreak policy is a necessary player
OL,8,Fsafety measure due to extreme
OL,9,Ftemperatures in the USA and Mexico `
OL,10,Ftwo of the three host nations ` this
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,FBut the move has faced criticism from
OL,14,Fsome, who argue that the initiative
OL,15,Fhas commercial motivations as well as
OL,16,Fones based on player welfare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
