FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,FFormer Arsenal and England forward Ian
OL,7,FWright said: "I just feel like it's
OL,8,Fanother way to get adverts into
OL,9,Fit...they've used the fact it's for
OL,10,Fthe players and for the hydration, not
OL,11,Ffor me."
OL,13,FThough British broadcasters haven't
OL,14,Fbeen cutting to adverts, American
OL,15,Fchannels like Fox have been using them
OL,16,Ffor full-screen commercial breaks.
OL,18,FThe breaks have also been criticised
OL,19,Ffor disrupting game momentum and
OL,20,Fgiving coaches opportunities to make
OL,21,Fregular tactical changes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
