OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,FFormer Chelsea women's manager, Emma
OL,7,FHayes, told ITV Sport on Sunday: "One
OL,8,Fof the beautiful things about football
OL,9,Fhas always been that there is one
OL,10,Fbreak."
OL,12,F"It's not like the NBA or NFL, it is
OL,13,Fundeniable, it's a coach's game this
OL,14,FWorld Cup, and you'll have analysts
OL,15,Fsending down three or four clips with
OL,16,Ftactical adaptations."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
