PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,FIn Brazil's game against Morocco, on
OL,7,FSaturday, coach Carlo Ancelotti used
OL,8,Fthe water break to his advantage,
OL,9,Faccording to Hayes, allowing the South
OL,10,FAmerican side to claw back against
OL,11,Ftheir North African opponents.
OL,13,F"You see (Carlos) Ancelotti make it in
OL,14,Fthe first half by moving Paqueta
OL,15,Finside which made a difference because
OL,16,Fthey'd lost a grip of the game in the
OL,17,Ffirst 25 minutes," she said.
OL,26,@uD@JpmuD@QpnvD@`rp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781569068
OL,3,CVirgil van Dijk says World Cup cooling
OL,4,Cbreaks should be decided 'game by game'
OL,6,F"We've seen it with every manager so
OL,7,Ffar that coaching comes into play, and
OL,8,Fit is so advantageous for the team
OL,9,Fthat is losing momentum.
OL,11,F"That's why I call them momentum
OL,12,Fbreaks. If you're on top, you don't
OL,13,Fwant it. If you're not, you won't mind
OL,14,Fit."
OL,16,FGermany coach Julian Nagelsmann also
OL,17,Findicated that the three-minute period
OL,18,Fhelped his team sort themselves out
OL,19,Ftactically after conceding a first-
OL,20,Fhalf equaliser in their 7-1 win over
OL,21,FCuracao on Sunday.
OL,26,@}D@E{q
